{"tid":1413561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應對政府民意戰方法","createTime":"2019-08-05T10:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:15:14.000Z","uid":48390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38890fe1e72a715661672892cfa3b8a0fcd6ae2e","tid":1413561,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"今朝林鄭記招內容概要：<br />\n<br />\n1.集中講經濟民生點受影響、幾多人手停口停，其他一概唔理<br />\n2.再配合財政司一輪經濟數據恐嚇<br />\n3.最後配合以每日開記招方式比TVB密集式洗腦<br />\n<br />\n繼朝早林奠記者會開始集中火力以經濟下行恐嚇市民後，下午警察記招亦將將兩個月以來發生嘅所有衰嘢賴落示威者到，指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n我地聽到故然覺得戇鳩，但記招內容唔係講比我地聽 － 係留比TVB同建制網媒造新聞用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要應對民意戰，暫時最有效最簡單就係大家如果同家人同住，就<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即剷哂電視機所有TVB台</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小呢一步，每個人行一步，起碼可以影響兩個人（父母）。冇左傳播途徑，咩propaganda都冇用"},{"pid":"99d452bb09a272e8f62260364da8309205485b60","tid":1413561,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1116a5419564ecc090fc5bd9b0a44ba737773b7","tid":1413561,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3fb90c25fa9ade8b0af950bd6f414ad4637d87","tid":1413561,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e876b4de24c46963e3926e07e4b56c0f007f5959","tid":1413561,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9813785a556b410f478fc61667d7a08912103cb","tid":1413561,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dcbed5cdf08ea6b01b862053088b4f1515d048","tid":1